{"tid":1872061,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"二手成交：擎天半島賣1950萬元 回到三年前水平","createTime":"2020-02-10T00:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T14:56:40.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c47d48320d3286e3a0003d027366702a219d4bcc","tid":1872061,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T00:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pTD0mK5OD7_PsPefjTG0ig--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/47641a6e45fcc64ef8c6638de829de07\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpTD0mK5OD7_PsPefjTG0ig--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F47641a6e45fcc64ef8c6638de829de07&h=4a66c243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美聯物業營業經理施蒂文表示，九龍站擎天半島6座高層H室，實用面積757方呎，單位座向東北，享部分山景及海景，獲外區用家以1,950萬元交吉購入，成交呎價25,760元。該單位早前叫價2,400萬元，1月份時減價至2,200萬元，最終再度下調意向價促成交易，累積減價約450萬元或約19%。<br />\n<br />\n他又指出，原業主於2009年以880萬元購入上址，即持貨約十年帳賺1.2倍。他補充，2017年同類型單位成交價約2,000萬元，即新成交價回到三年前水平。"},{"pid":"737a360a28c94a48d31d8b0756be2eaac3abcc3a","tid":1872061,"uid":161726,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c47d48320d3286e3a0003d027366702a219d4bcc","tid":1872061,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T00:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pTD0mK5OD7_PsPefjTG0ig--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/47641a6e45fcc64ef8c6638de829de07\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpTD0mK5OD7_PsPefjTG0ig--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F47641a6e45fcc64ef8c6638de829de07&h=4a66c243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美聯物業營業經理施蒂文表示，九龍站擎天半島6座高層H室，實用面積757方呎，單位座向東北，享部分山景及海景，獲外區用家以1,950萬元交吉購入，成交呎價25,760元。該單位早前叫價2,400萬元，1月份時減價至2,200萬元，最終再度下調